{"tid":2358491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反侵還反侵，唔代科技巨頭做得無錯","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:00:25.000Z","uid":210140,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb3fe87d4b2188742019689baeb72c4d21fa53a","tid":2358491,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"我已經唔計封鎖侵侵帳號，你話佢煽動叛亂又好，放假消息又好<br />\n如果同一標準，點解唔封鎖埋中共大外宣，五毛小粉紅既帳號<br />\n然後呢兩年來不斷封鎖黃陣營既專頁同群組，壓低宣傳度<br />\n然後而家同我大大聲拎住枝民主言論自由既旗？無野啊？<br />\n我呼籲各位左翼，即使侵落台，亦都要針住呢班科技巨頭同傳媒<br />\n呢班人既雙重標準令我非常嘔心<br />\n緊記，敵人既敵人未必係朋友，<br />\n朝你選擇因為佢反侵而放佢地一馬，他朝君體也相同"},{"pid":"ae5c6cfac8bd57bfd80e80a12552de15a5c3a441","tid":2358491,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21831a6fd67d5290f2d2e8d7a3afcb345b8c96a8","tid":2358491,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a903bef8350d51126ec05aa1163a466c2a3a9739","tid":2358491,"uid":10466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"算把啦，佢哋唔會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbac215a58496277672174ce5a889cadb5c812a","tid":2358491,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134a328eb3b24dc66ff89bfb2595a85a3532461f","tid":2358491,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"BLM個啲唔計煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f403e1208aabc13bef0fb521e0862a68580e40","tid":2358491,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"左膠表示應該嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a